title: Another beginning with the Guhuo bird
description: Another beginning with the Guhuo bird Free Manhua Li Yan, who is contracted with an incurable disease, by chance, entered a bizarre and motley world ” Yanfu “. Relying on his masterly skills, he step by step become a person of strong character. And in the process of walking through the world of Yanfu, he also began to discover the true mysteries of this world.
